<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371304" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Kanye-Gospel-Davido.jpg?resize=1280%2C720&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="1280" height="720" data-recalc-dims="1" />Kanye West, ever the sampler, did a gospel cover of Davido‘s “IF” for his most recent Sunday Service at the City of Refuge church in Los Angeles. The rapper, who has been consistent with his Sunday services, also covered Beyoncé and Wizkid‘s “Brown Skin Girl” during the service, segueing from it to “IF.” Watch the full service below, but you can skip over to 1:21:00 for the “Brown Skin Girl” cover, and 1:24:00 for the “IF” cover. The post You Should Watch Kanye West’s Gospel Cover of Davido’s “IF” for his Sunday Service  Source: Bella Naija